{"tid":1855164,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"《劉伯溫碑記》  預言分析","createTime":"2020-02-01T02:51:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-10T11:31:12.000Z","uid":91648,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"774290500c5a2fcb3258b9d37b2f3aba6ea0cc5e","tid":1855164,"uid":91648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T02:51:29.000Z","msg":"《劉伯溫碑記》  <br />\n  天有眼，地有眼，人人都有一雙眼，<br />\n  天也翻，地也翻，逍遙自在樂無邊，<br />\n  <strong>貧者一萬留一千，富者一萬留二三，</strong><br />\n  貧富若不回心轉，看看死期在眼前，<br />\n  平地無有五穀種， <strong>謹防四野絕人煙</strong>，<br />\n  若問<strong>瘟疫何時現</strong>，但看<strong>九冬十月間</strong>，<br />\n  行善之人得一見，作惡之人不得觀，<br />\n  世上有人行大善，遭了此劫不上算，<br />\n  還有十愁在眼前：<br />\n  一愁<strong>天下亂紛紛</strong>，二愁東西餓死人，<br />\n  三愁<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">湖廣</span></strong>遭大難，四愁各省起狼煙，<br />\n  五愁人民不安然，六愁九冬十月間，<br />\n  七愁<strong>有飯無人食</strong>，八愁<strong>有人無衣穿</strong>，<br />\n  九愁<span style=\"color: red;\">屍體無人檢</span>，十愁難過<span style=\"color: red;\">豬鼠年</span>， <span style=\"color: blue;\">（2020）</span><br />\n  <span style=\"color: brown;\">若得過了大劫年，才算世間不老仙</span>，<br />\n  就是銅打鐵羅漢， 難過<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">七月初一十三</span></strong>，  （註：2020年農曆七月是死亡高峰期）<br />\n  任你金剛鐵羅漢，除非善乃能保全，<br />\n  謹防人人艱難過，關過天番<strong>龍蛇年</strong>，<span style=\"color: blue;\">（註：2024至2025可望有改善）</span><br />\n  幼兒好似朱洪武，四川更比漢中苦，<br />\n  大獅吼如雷，勝過悼百虎，<br />\n  犀牛現出尾，平地遇猛若，<br />\n  若問大平年，架橋迎新主，<br />\n  上元甲子到，人人哈哈笑，<br />\n  問他笑什麼？<strong>迎接新地主</strong>，<br />\n  上管三尺日，夜無盜賊難，<br />\n  雖是謀為主，主坐中央土。<br />\n  人民喊真主：<br />\n  銀錢是個寶，看破用不了，<br />\n  果然是個寶，地下裂不倒。<br />\n  七人一路走，引誘進了口，<br />\n  三點加一勾，八王二十口，  <span style=\"color: blue;\">（ 「善」字）</span><br />\n  人人喜笑，個個平安。<br />\n  人人可觀，個個可傳，<br />\n  有人印送，勿取金錢。<br />\n  行善者可保，作惡者難逃。<br />\n  敬重天地神明父母，<strong>惜字紙五穀</strong>。<br />\n  謹當切記。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79ba8351fba855a173be497cd154920ed17c8f55","tid":1855164,"uid":91648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T02:53:27.000Z","msg":"大家留名，睇睇農曆7月咩環境....."},{"pid":"f0f7515f3c6c030cac35722cee7ccd6320aa34e4","tid":1855164,"uid":181789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T02:54:19.000Z","msg":"留名....."},{"pid":"8e69bc491b786912f2730c1a27b51d379440c0c6","tid":1855164,"uid":91648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"79ba8351fba855a173be497cd154920ed17c8f55","tid":1855164,"uid":91648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T02:53:27.000Z","msg":"大家留名，睇睇農曆7月咩環境....."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T02:55:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f12943b1c053d5f81b0ed202de12828e36e82051","tid":1855164,"uid":285514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T02:56:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2f9cb4190890235424357850fe5e81572f10f72","tid":1855164,"uid":242537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T04:25:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a718f2b9b28fb190fdb7d4c9999014a206c2c93a","tid":1855164,"uid":91648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T04:56:20.000Z","msg":"負評"},{"pid":"9f4413cf5caac2bcee42a03301d4c76051b033ce","tid":1855164,"uid":19037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T07:53:07.000Z","msg":"人人都有一雙眼&lt; 似描述緊個個人都戴緊口罩"},{"pid":"02d1b8d06f60c2e8d4309ae2f44d2968422ace98","tid":1855164,"uid":122896,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T08:57:26.000Z","msg":"真<br />\n善<br />\n忍"